INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install
    make clean

REQUIREMENTS

    * openssl
    * gpg
    * mod_perl (mod-perl2)
    * perl-libwww

USING IN DEVELOPMENT MODE

    0. Set PERL5LIB
       export PERL5LIB=/home/user/modules/MToken/lib

    1. Initialize project
       perl bin/mtoken -d -D foo init myfooproject

    2. Make
       cd foo
       perl Makefile.PL
       make
       make test
       make clean

    3. Debugging
       perl Makefile.PL
       make init
       make test
       make clean
